Package MDL

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    All
    All echoes the name of every program that can be invoked in MDL* Simple enough to enumerate
    InstanceOf
    InstanceOf is a program that takes two inputs, a schema and a db, and confirms (or refutes) that the db conforms to the schema (sans constraints)
    OO2schema
    OO2Schema translates S.ooschema.pl to S.schema.pl that is, it propagates supertable attributes to subtable attributes
    ReadDB
    MDL program that reads a database file and reports errors (other than constraint violations)
    ReadSC
    reads a schema or ooschema and reports errors
    VerifyInstall
    program that sees if it can invoke Violet
    Version
    MDL program that outputs the version of MDELite
    Violet
    MDL program that invokes Violet
    VioletClassParser
    invokes VioletClassParser
    VioletClassUnParser
    invokes violet class unparser
    Vm2t
    MDL program to invoke Velocity
    YumlClassParser
    MDL program to invoke YumlClassParser
    YumlClassUnParser
    MDL program to invoke Yuml Class Unparser
